## Method
Weight each finding by (a) mechanism strength — is the failure mechanism concretely demonstrated,
not just asserted? — and (b) cost-to-defer — what does it cost if we ship without fixing it?
Do NOT rank by how many reviewers raised it. A single reviewer's deep, well-mechanism'd finding
outranks a shallow finding both raised. (source label = which lens, NOT a vote weight.)

## Blockers (fix before merge — strong mechanism AND high cost-to-defer)
